[
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000002_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000002_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "Every preparation had been completed the day before, all of us having worked like galley slaves to achieve this result, as soon as it became apparent that launching on this day might be possible.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "Nature appeared in fact to have arrayed herself in gala attire, in honour of the occasion.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "This occupied the two mates until breakfast was ready, when we all sat down to the meal in most exuberant spirits.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "When we had all taken our stations-",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "\"Is everybody ready?\" inquired my father.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "\"Then knock away with a will, lads!\" exclaimed the skipper.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "The schooner clove the water smoothly and easily as she drove astern when once fairly afloat, and held her way long enough to shoot far beyond her consorts at anchor in the bay.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "As soon as her speed was sufficiently reduced, Bob let go his anchor, and we had the satisfaction of seeing that she floated lightly and on a perfectly even keel.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "When we had admired the schooner to our hearts' content, my father wished to know whether any one had any proposal to make as to the manner in which the remainder of the day should be spent.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "I was delighted to observe that both my father and Winter keenly enjoyed this short cruise outside.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "Having made the tour of the island both outside and inside the reef, and admired its many beauties, we at length sat down to our meal in high spirits, and with appetites which enabled us to do the most ample justice to Ella's bounteous provision, which, it now appeared, had been in progress the whole of the previous day, in anticipation of some such arrangement as that which she had proposed.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "I had noticed an unusual flutter in the dear little girl's manner more than once during the morning, as well as considerable imperfectly repressed excitement; but I had said nothing to her about it, attributing it to that which had produced so much excitement of feeling among the rest of us, namely, the important event of the launch.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000025_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000025_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "This feeling of excitement still continued to animate us; but, strangely enough, Ella seemed the least able of the party to control it, and it appeared to have the effect of agitating her nerves considerably. Moreover, she seemed to be singularly pre occupied over something, answering remarks at random-sometimes when she was not addressed at all-and then flushing up and apologising confusedly.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000027_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000027_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "We also decided upon certain rendezvous in case of being compelled, by bad weather, to part company at any particular part of the voyage.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "When this topic seemed pretty well exhausted, Ella remarked nervously, \"It seems then, Harry, that you have quite given up the idea of making any further search for the treasure island.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000028_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000028_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "I have not heard it mentioned once for-oh! ever so long.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000034_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000034_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "\"Somewhat like these that we are sitting under at this moment?\" interrupted Ella excitedly.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000037_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000037_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "We sprang to our feet as one man, infinitely more excited even than Ella was, and walked up to the tree and carefully examined the mark.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000039_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000039_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "\"Here it is,\" again exclaimed Ella, darting to a tree which stood on the edge of the clump, and again pointing out a mark very similar to the first.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000040_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000040_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "Of the nature of this mark, too, there could be no possible doubt.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000040_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000040_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "I then drove the stick I held in my hand deep into the sandy beach, exclaiming, \"Here lies the buried treasure ship, if there be any truth in the story.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000041_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000041_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "\"Here, you two niggers, jump into this here canoe and paddle me down to the cutter as quick as you knows how.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000042_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000042_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "Their number had impressed itself upon her, and, endeavouring to remember what it was she had heard or dreamed connected with seven cocoa nut trees, the story of the treasure had suddenly flashed across her mind.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000042_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000042_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "And upon this resolution had been based her plot for the picnic.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000043_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000043_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "I am so happy, dearest, for I do not think I could have endured that.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000045_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000045_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "Bob soon returned with a couple of shovels, and, springing ashore from the canoe, he handed one to Winter, and began at once to ply the other most vigorously himself, exclaiming as he did so:",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000046_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000046_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "\"There you are, my lad: now fire away as hard as you like.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000047_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000047_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "The two men worked with a will, and soon stood in a good sized hole, about three feet deep, whilst the rest of us looked on at their labours with the keenest interest.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000047_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000047_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "At length Winter's shovel struck upon something hard, and he announced the fact with a joyous shout.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000047_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000047_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "A few more strokes of Winter's shovel laid bare a small patch of damp discoloured planking, a further proof, if we needed one, of the truth of the story.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000047_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000047_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "Bob was still digging away as hard as ever. Presently he ceased digging, and began shovelling the loose sand off a piece of the deck or something else which he had got down to.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000048_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000048_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "This accomplished, it was found that we had been so fortunate as to hit, at the first trial, upon the hole through which the Spaniard had penetrated to the innermost recesses of the ship.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000048_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000048_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "He and Winter were both working under the influence of powerful excitement, so it was not long before they had cleared away the sand sufficiently to enable them to lay hold of and drag forth an ingot, black and discoloured almost as rusty iron, but heavy enough to prove most satisfactorily that it was not that metal.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000051_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000051_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "The next day saw us hard at work again, and, not to dwell too long upon matters which may be passed over briefly, in three days we had the box of gems, and as much gold as we considered we could take.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000051_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000051_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "I here had an opportunity of acquainting the proper authorities with all the circumstances connected with the destruction of the pirate brig, and of the crew being imprisoned on the island, and I afterwards learned that a cruiser had been despatched to the spot, and that the entire band were captured, tried, condemned upon a mass of evidence, which was soon collected against them, and hanged.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000052_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000052_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "All the ships, without exception, were dressed with flags, and there was a long article in one of the local papers headed, \"Thrilling Romance of the Sea,\" in which the story of Ella's rescue from the wreck told with great effect.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000053_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000053_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "Here we again filled up provisions and water, and once more despatched letters home.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000054_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000054_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "By the time that we had done what we wanted, the gale was over, and we lost no time in making a fresh start.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000054_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000054_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "We soon got into the south-east trades, and, as they happened to be blowing strong, we made the best of them, and did not attempt to stop at Saint Helena.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000054_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000054_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "We were fortunate again in crossing the line, getting a little slant of wind, which carried us handsomely across the usually calm belt which so tries the patience of the homeward bound seaman at that spot; and after a remarkably fine passage of thirty nine days from Table Bay, we found ourselves at anchor in Funchal Roads.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000059_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000059_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "I will pass over in silence the rapturous meeting which ensued, for the feelings of all were of too deep and sacred a character for so inexperienced a pen as mine to deal with.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5977_46900_000059_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5977/46900/5977_46900_000059_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5977",
        "content": "Suffice it to say that we all enjoyed on that evening one of those short seasons of perfect, unalloyed happiness which are occasionally permitted even here on earth.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
